2333
01:32:18,320 --> 01:32:19,980
A particle moves in the gravity of a picture.

2334
01:32:20,260 --> 01:32:21,380
It's a random particle.

2335
01:32:21,760 --> 01:32:22,920
It's a skeeter here.

2336
01:32:23,460 --> 01:32:24,660
It's right in the Lagrangian.

2337
01:32:25,140 --> 01:32:25,880
It's a mayfly.

2338
01:32:26,560 --> 01:32:27,620
It's not a mayfly.

